# Dodgy Game 🎮

A simple 2D arcade-style game developed using the Godot Engine, where the player must avoid obstacles and survive as long as possible.

## 🚀 Features
- Player movement controls
- Collision detection system
- Basic game mechanics
- Increasing difficulty (optional if added)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Godot Engine
- GDScript

## 🎯 Objective
Control the player and dodge obstacles to achieve the highest possible score.

## 📌 Future Improvements
- Add scoring system
- Game over screen
- Restart functionality
- Improved UI/UX

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the project in Godot Engine
3. Run the main scene

